Usage:
  llm-proxy [command]

Available Commands:
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  help        Help about any command
  run         Run various services

Flags:
  -h, --help                help for llm-proxy
      --log-format string   Log format: text, json (default: text if interactive, json otherwise)
      --log-level string    Log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")

Use "llm-proxy [command] --help" for more information about a command.
